2025-08-05 12:19:33 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1754396373,"user_id":18638,"user_ip":"83.24.55.89","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:141.0) Gecko\/20100101 Firefox\/141.0","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":11107,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"100","author_id":18638,"project_id":"1701","nick":"Ma\u0142gorzata","topic":"U\u0142o\u017cenie pokoi","content":"Dzie\u0144 dobry, jest mo\u017cliwo\u015b\u0107 \u017ce tak powiem odwr\u00f3cenia pomieszcze\u0144 w odbiciu lustrzanym tylko wed\u0142ug osi wzd\u0142u\u017c budynku (d\u0142u\u017cszej \u015bciany domu). Chcemy wybudowa\u0107 ten projekt ale u\u0142o\u017cenie pokoi nie pasuje do na\u015bwietlenia dzia\u0142ki. Zale\u017cy nam najbardziej na zamienieniu miejscami sypialni z schodami i \u0142azienkami ale jakby da\u0142o si\u0119 zamieni\u0107 salon z kuchni\u0105 te\u017c by\u015bmy nie pogardzili :)","create_date":"2025-08-05 12:19:33","modify_date":"2025-08-05 12:19:33","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2843439},"entity_changes":false}
